summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 221E page 8, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in East 120' of Lot 13, Block 5, Cedar Park Add., located on the northwest corner of 35th Ave. N.E. and E. 125th St., from Duplex Residence Medium Density (RD 7200) Zone to Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone.
